Liverpool winger Jordan Ibe has been out of action for six weeks with a knee ligament injury . 
  The 19-year-old damaged his knee ligaments against Besiktas in the Europa League . 
  Brendan Rodgers will include Ibe in his squad to face Newcastle on Monday . 
  Mario Balotelli remains sidelined with illness . 
  Liverpool beat Blackburn Rovers in the FA Cup on Wednesday . 
 